{
  "stem": "24885.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- I mean it showed Kristallnacht and all this stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were-- you were discriminated against in school and wherever you went on a large scale.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't do this because you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were verboten, forbidden to go to college.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Poland, while it was true they didn't allow Jews to go to medical school or, or, or lawyer school or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But a lot of them, they took a certain percentage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my two cousins in Radom, Sam, his sisters, younger sisters went to college, graduated, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes, they were far or few in between, but some of them were accepted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in Germany it put a stop to everything after Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The joke was going back to Poland he says, do we have enough to eat?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did we have a good life?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, it wasn't for everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a lot of poor people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were poor because the country was poor and discriminated, and you didn't have a chance to grow, to get an education.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can remember the elder people talk and a lot of people who escaped from Poland either they go bankrupt or they embezzled something or so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But otherwise, if you wanted to work, you could make a living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, how true it was, I don't know anymore because there was hatred.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The church hated us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know there's a man right here has two brothers from Florida-- in Florida from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're both college graduates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their father was a chemist in the leather factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The original name was Lip-- as a matter of fact, he puts a magazine out now.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
